{"tid":1202691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"航空界嘅你地 唔好再猶豫喇","createTime":"2019-06-11T10:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T04:52:59.000Z","uid":15027,"like":134,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c5be1b3ed9adbad6ee2cfc2a16e8597f3e344f16","tid":1202691,"uid":15027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:08:30.000Z","msg":"講罷工，最有影響力嘅一定係你地。<br />\n<br />\n所以真係希望你地唔好再猶豫<br />\n<br />\n亦希望你地可以團結下<br />\n<br />\n不論<br />\n天空嘅機師空姐<br />\n地下嘅地勤人員operation嘅你<br />\n<br />\n係大是大非之下 唔好再考慮d咩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我唔返工咪其他人做埋我果份<br />\n驚影響到其他同事呀<br />\n之後實會比人針對啦</span><br />\n呢啲廢話<br />\n<br />\n唔好低估左你地嘅影響力<br />\n機場嘅小混亂 真係可以做成好多連帶嘅效果<br />\n<br />\n唔係一定要你地上街 當然可以嘅話緊係最好<br />\n只係想你地可以表下態 <br />\n同時可以話比全世界聽我地嘅訴求<br />\n<br />\n咁多抗爭者受皮肉甚至牢獄之苦<br />\n甚至好多青少年為左我地嘅香港<br />\n冒住要犧牲自己前途嘅情況下<br />\n<br />\n返少一日工射個波只係微不足道嘅犧牲<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"6d93fdce53e66dd2dacd5b04a6a2de523d054b21","tid":1202691,"uid":62424,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:09:58.000Z","msg":"仲有機場保安呀"},{"pid":"879f1e8dfedbde66a8cebdb810234c7e5dab48f5","tid":1202691,"uid":157362,"like":3,"dislike":50,"score":-47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:10:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98a59cbe834ed5a620533ac1174961fb96cd1507","tid":1202691,"uid":15027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"879f1e8dfedbde66a8cebdb810234c7e5dab48f5","tid":1202691,"uid":157362,"like":3,"dislike":50,"score":-47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:10:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:15:16.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"4ce0a43099b66d1394bb8963a56be04fa35b395f","tid":1202691,"uid":254594,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"879f1e8dfedbde66a8cebdb810234c7e5dab48f5","tid":1202691,"uid":157362,"like":3,"dislike":50,"score":-47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:10:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:16:19.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n去唔成出金鐘幫手<img 